86
00:10:44,310 --> 00:10:46,610
<i>Oh, kakav nered.</i>

87
00:10:46,710 --> 00:10:49,720
<i>Magoo. Bok, Magoo.</i>

88
00:10:50,220 --> 00:10:51,620
