98
00:11:23,120 --> 00:11:25,520
Zašto želiš znati takve stvari?

99
00:11:27,320 --> 00:11:28,520
Ja sam bluesman.

100
00:11:28,720 --> 00:11:31,920
Bluesman.

101
00:11:32,120 --> 00:11:33,930
